<L>__{exterior street short time later}
<A>__{roper is exiting the bank and putting back on his gun when he hears the sound of a camera shutter. he turns to see veronica (ronnie) tate holding the camera. she snaps one of roper with earl in the b.g. being placed in a squad car.}
<C>__{ronnie}
<D>__{there's one for the front page.}
